{"tid":2450023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾接種疫苗男督察確診　或接種前已感染","createTime":"2021-03-17T05:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T07:19:48.000Z","uid":286206,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa94817a99f353a9b51c6beeb0428baa89d9a80","tid":2450023,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名38歲居於何文田督察級警察宿舍C座的男督察，前日證實確診感染新型冠狀病毒，41歲太太及2名女兒亦同樣確診。消息指，確診督察上星期五因獲悉女兒一名同學確診，全家前往檢測，督察當天亦預約接種科興疫苗，到前日檢測證實全家確診，估計督察在接種疫苗前已受感染。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，接種疫苗情況由衛生部門交代，而確診的男督察過去14日無外遊記錄，工作期間有佩戴口罩，並無同公眾接觸。他最後一日上班日為本月12日。警方高度關注事件，與事主可能有緊密接觸的警務人員及文職人員，都會安排接受病毒檢測，而督察工作的地方會進行清潔及消毒。"},{"pid":"930d342621dcbe1c98a7a0aa71ce205f3a7abdb7","tid":2450023,"uid":25952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:50:15.000Z","msg":"毒溝毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次仲唔死"},{"pid":"d364e617819a53f68da355870a76fc965e34ce70","tid":2450023,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"只可以咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02883ac4c59dfcc1cce31004d1cb86f840fc0993","tid":2450023,"uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:52:28.000Z","msg":"咁去佢打針果個中心 果D人係咪要強檢呀！"},{"pid":"24bb76762a920259d4445033d1361f4182324aab","tid":2450023,"uid":286206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:53:06.000Z","msg":"建議再拍多兩支應該藥到病除<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5375e23a6f21277771136adc04de0c550c7a8c","tid":2450023,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:53:11.000Z","msg":"呢獲真係死全家"},{"pid":"ec32e1e163c9c7d409f191d48e3b4ee5d4f1ad0c","tid":2450023,"uid":260005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202